Seibert Says Germany to Take Right Steps to Recapitalize Banks

-- B y   L e o n   M a n g a s a r i a n
-- 
2011-10-14T09:56:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/seibert-says-germany-to-take-right-steps-to-recapitalize-banks.html
Chancellor Angela Merkel ’s spokesman
Steffen Seibert said  Germany  will take “the right steps” to
recapitalize banks.  “When a recapitalization is necessary, we have to take the
right steps,” Seibert told reporters today in Berlin without
giving any details.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Leon Mangasarian at 
 lmangasarian@bloomberg.net  